---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="SME EU AI Act Compliance | AiLex Consulting | UK SME Implementation Framework"
  description="Systematic regulatory compliance methodology designed for UK SMEs without internal compliance resources. Emergency assessment and implementation support for EU AI Act requirements."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Professional Hero -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-50 to-blue-50 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 tracking-wider">SCIENTIA ET LEX</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-6">
            SME EU AI Act Compliance
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Systematic regulatory compliance methodology designed for UK SMEs without internal compliance resources. Emergency assessment and implementation support delivering comprehensive EU AI Act compliance within 6-10 weeks.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700">€35M</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Maximum penalty</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">6-10 Weeks</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Implementation timeline</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">No Teams</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Internal hiring required</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SME Challenges -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-4">What regulatory challenges do SMEs face with the EU AI Act?</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Complex Framework</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">99 articles across 180 pages requiring specialist interpretation and systematic application for SME operations</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Resource Constraints</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Limited internal expertise necessitating external regulatory guidance and implementation support</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Penalty Exposure</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Enforcement penalties reaching 7% annual turnover or €35M, requiring immediate compliance action</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SME Methodology -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-4">How does our SME compliance methodology work?</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700 min-w-[60px]">01</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Emergency Assessment</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
                  <div>
                    <strong>Regulatory Analysis:</strong> Complete AI system discovery, risk classification using Claude AI-enhanced methodology, GPAI compliance evaluation, regulatory gap analysis
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <strong>Professional Deliverables:</strong> Comprehensive assessment report, prioritised compliance roadmap, immediate risk mitigation recommendations, implementation pathway options
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700 min-w-[60px]">02</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Implementation Support</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
                  <div>
                    <strong>Systematic Implementation:</strong> Documentation framework development, process design with minimal disruption, team training and capability transfer, compliance monitoring setup
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <strong>SME-Optimised Approach:</strong> No internal compliance hiring, streamlined processes fitting existing operations, clear handover with maintenance guidance, flexible engagement terms
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700 min-w-[60px]">03</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Fractional CAIO Service</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
                  <div>
                    <strong>Ongoing Compliance:</strong> Monthly compliance health monitoring, regulatory update assessment, new AI system evaluation, strategic AI governance guidance
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <strong>Executive Advisory Value:</strong> Chief AI Officer expertise without permanent hire, on-demand strategic support, continuous regulatory protection, competitive advantage development
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-4">SME Compliance Implementation</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can SMEs achieve EU AI Act compliance without internal expertise?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">SMEs successfully achieve comprehensive compliance through systematic external methodology combined with minimal internal resource commitment. Our 6-day emergency assessment identifies requirements, whilst implementation support establishes operational compliance without permanent hiring.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">How long does SME compliance implementation typically require?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Complete SME compliance implementation ranges from 6-10 weeks, beginning with emergency assessment and progressing through systematic documentation and process establishment. Timeline varies according to AI system complexity and existing organisational capabilities.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">What ongoing compliance maintenance do SMEs require?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">SMEs maintain compliance through quarterly monitoring, regulatory update assessment, and new AI system evaluation. Fractional CAIO service provides systematic oversight without permanent executive recruitment, ensuring continuous compliance and strategic guidance.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">What investment does SME compliance require versus penalty risk?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">SME compliance investment typically ranges £15,000-25,000 for complete implementation, representing 0.04-0.07% of maximum penalty exposure (€35M or 7% turnover). Emergency assessment (£9,500) provides immediate risk mitigation and implementation roadmap.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Professional Consultation -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-slate-900 text-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-6">Request Professional Consultation</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Begin systematic EU AI Act compliance with emergency assessment and comprehensive implementation support designed specifically for UK SME operations.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4 md:flex md:justify-center">
          <a href="/emergency-assessment" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-colors">
            Emergency Assessment
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-colors">
            Implementation Support
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mt-6 text-sm">Flexible payment terms • Initial consultation without commitment</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <!-- Schema Markup -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can SMEs achieve EU AI Act compliance without internal expertise?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "SMEs successfully achieve comprehensive compliance through systematic external methodology combined with minimal internal resource commitment. Our 6-day emergency assessment identifies requirements, whilst implementation support establishes operational compliance without permanent hiring."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question", 
        "name": "How long does SME compliance implementation typically require?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Complete SME compliance implementation ranges from 6-10 weeks, beginning with emergency assessment and progressing through systematic documentation and process establishment. Timeline varies according to AI system complexity and existing organisational capabilities."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What ongoing compliance maintenance do SMEs require?", 
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "SMEs maintain compliance through quarterly monitoring, regulatory update assessment, and new AI system evaluation. Fractional CAIO service provides systematic oversight without permanent executive recruitment, ensuring continuous compliance and strategic guidance."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What investment does SME compliance require versus penalty risk?", 
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "SME compliance investment typically ranges £15,000-25,000 for complete implementation, representing 0.04-0.07% of maximum penalty exposure (€35M or 7% turnover). Emergency assessment (£9,500) provides immediate risk mitigation and implementation roadmap."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .font-serif { font-family: Georgia, serif; }
</style>